
extends layout

block content
	div.container(style='margin:20px')
	h3 Order your documents
	p You can order your PDF files and also specify the pages that you want to use in your final document. Once you finish, click the 'Compile' button in the top bar. Check your email after a couple of minutes, you will receive the document in your inbox.
		ul#sortable
			- for (var i = 0; i < files.length; i++)
				li
					h4(style='margin:10px')= files[i]
					label.control-label(for='name-tf') From page
					.controls
						input#name-tf(type='number', name='fromPage', value= '0')
					label.control-label(for='name-tf') To page
					.controls
						input#name-tf(type='number', name='toPage', value= '0')